{"TopicId":136016,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"[ASC-III] Air Superiority Challenge - King of the Hill (BDArmory 4v4 AI Duels: WW1 Theme) - Now Concluded!","CreatedByName":"inigma","CreatedById":69310,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-04T07:54:02Z","PageNum":33,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Monkey29399","CreatedById":152442,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-21T14:27:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222527732\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461243908\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhey, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69310-inigma/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269310\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69310-inigma/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@inigma\u003C/a\u003E, can you give me a ping 24 hours before my match? I want to update my fighter, but I don\u0027t want to post the updated version yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame here. I still need to make a few tweaks to my fighter design before the match starts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuicidalInsanity","CreatedById":143878,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-21T18:50:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat was an interesting battle. Apparently ablative wingmen make the best armor. I\u0027m not sure how or why the VulTurRaptors were only targeting one plane most of the time, but it would be interesting if it could be replicated with other craft, especially in light of being able to submit two craft for the ASC; i can see this glitch? exploit? AI quirk? becoming a design consideration for future entries.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRest in peace, VulTurRaptor, you were a worthy and truly formidable adversary.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NotAnAimbot","CreatedById":151034,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-21T19:56:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome music \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69310-inigma/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269310\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69310-inigma/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@inigma\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/QCy68CWDKVE?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/FIcxqVRLEWI?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jrodriguez","CreatedById":130617,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-21T20:55:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey guys, I\u0027m doing crazy combats in KSP 1.1. Check my drones vs X-Wings battle!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/W-HiDFesIg4?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"drtricky","CreatedById":154647,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-21T22:43:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69310-inigma/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269310\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69310-inigma/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@inigma\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Is BDA working fine in 1.1?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-21T23:27:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222527551\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461237360\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161616\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jakerblam22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Jakerblam22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm. maybe my .50 cals weren\u0027t set up right, they never seemed to do any real damage.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI place two on the underside of the plane, and two on the upper side- one pair on each wing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"inigma","CreatedById":69310,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-21T23:35:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222529282\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461278599\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154647\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022drtricky\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n51 minutes ago, drtricky said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69310-inigma/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269310\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69310-inigma/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@inigma\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Is BDA working fine in 1.1?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMost likely. Hower ASC II won\u0027t start until ASC I is finished with the current roster.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jakerblam22","CreatedById":161616,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-21T23:35:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222529403\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461281229\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI place two on the underside of the plane, and two on the upper side- one pair on each wing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was using the Mark 1 cockpit (the pointy one) and I had 1 on each side of the nose. Maybe I\u0027ll resurrect that plane......\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-22T00:04:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222529428\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461281748\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161616\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jakerblam22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, Jakerblam22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was using the Mark 1 cockpit (the pointy one) and I had 1 on each side of the nose. Maybe I\u0027ll resurrect that plane......\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey move COM a lot, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jakerblam22","CreatedById":161616,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-22T00:17:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222529481\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461283465\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey move COM a lot, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I remember right, that plane was highly maneuverable and my first attempt at designing a plane for this challenge. Failed in testing, but now... maybe i could fix it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jrodriguez","CreatedById":130617,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-22T23:53:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003EKSP: ASC King of the Hill NotAnAimbot vs SuicidalInsanity\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/x9jKr8nFdMo?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Solarius III won the fight 3 - 0! How many lasers have you clipped together? 4, 8? hahaha\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NotAnAimbot","CreatedById":151034,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T01:52:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222532167\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461369196\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130617\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jrodriguez\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, jrodriguez said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Solarius III won the fight 3 - 0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStrange, sometimes the F-2 doesn\u0027t fire when the Solarius does. Guess it\u0027s back to missiles and lasers together.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess this will be the hard counter:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-6 AMRAAMS at 6M/T\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-AMRAAMS fire outside of laser range and make Sols go into evasive maneuvers\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Laser plane moves in to overheat evading Sol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-23T01:55:30Z\u0022 title=\u002204/23/2016 01:55  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 23, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by NotAnAimbot\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"drtricky","CreatedById":154647,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T06:00:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222532167\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461369196\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130617\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jrodriguez\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, jrodriguez said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many lasers have you clipped together? 4, 8? hahaha\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I was wondering how a single laser was so effective from over 4 km away.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI seriously think we should ban offensively oriented laser turrets in the next ASC, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-23T06:02:01Z\u0022 title=\u002204/23/2016 06:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 23, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by drtricky\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JollyGreenGI","CreatedById":70652,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T06:33:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRequesting to add a second fighter rather than two of the same:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/JollyGreenGI/TAM-Y22E-Fiesta-RIOT\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ETAM-Y22E \u0022Fiesta\u0022 RIOT\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hobbes Novakoff","CreatedById":129018,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T16:01:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222532805\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461391221\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154647\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022drtricky\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, drtricky said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI seriously think we should ban offensively oriented laser turrets in the next ASC, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI support that. BTW, once the hosts\u00A0clear the competitor backlog, we\u0027ll be starting in on ASC-II, which will be fought in 1.1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m also working on a new challenge: ASC-A, where you try to capture the island airfield against increasingly stiff resistance. It\u0027ll require a very different type of plane, and I\u0027m thinking of also making it a test of squadron command skills and manual piloting-depends on whether or not people want to self-host. Luckily, flak and SAM emplacements are 9 and 15 parts respectively, so I\u0027ll be able to put some crazy stuff later on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-23T16:04:10Z\u0022 title=\u002204/23/2016 04:04  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 23, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Hobbes Novakoff\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NotAnAimbot","CreatedById":151034,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T16:33:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222532805\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461391221\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154647\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022drtricky\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, drtricky said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthink we should ban offensively oriented laser turrets\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLaser turrets are fine, but not when spammed. Maybe limit the loadout to X number of turrets?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hobbes Novakoff","CreatedById":129018,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T16:36:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222533787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461429228\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022151034\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NotAnAimbot\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, NotAnAimbot said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLaser turrets are fine, but not when spammed. Maybe limit the loadout to X number of turrets?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn ASC-A, I\u0027m thinking of only allowing lasers if you are using the Mk3 cockpit.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NotAnAimbot","CreatedById":151034,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T16:46:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222533796\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461429407\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129018\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hobbes Novakoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Hobbes Novakoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nonly allowing lasers if you are using the Mk3 cockpit.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you think about this then?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-1.25 cockpits can only carry two .50s, 2 Vulcans or a single GAU-8\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Mk2 cockpits can carry two Vulcans turrets or two GAU-8s\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Mk3 cockpits can carry three GAU-8s, 4 Vulcan turrets or a single laser in the nose\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuicidalInsanity","CreatedById":143878,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T16:48:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222532167\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461369196\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130617\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jrodriguez\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, jrodriguez said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow many lasers have you clipped together? 4, 8? hahaha\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6 lasers, which are very much a double edged sword, and responsible for a number of exploitable flaws in the Solarius\u0027 design\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdvantages and flaws of the Solarius\u0027 design, as seen in the previous two videos:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLaser cluster Pros:\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnything that gets within 4-5 km, dies. Probably. \u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLaser cluster Cons:\u003Cbr\u003E\n5 tons of laser on the nose makes the Solarius fly like a three legged cow.\u003Cbr\u003E\nLack of maneuverability means anemic missile defense.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe laser cluster uses \u003Cem\u003E2100\u003C/em\u003E Ec/s\u003Cem\u003E. \u003C/em\u003EThere is about 5500 Ec worth of batteries on board.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe Solarius has no secondary armament.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo far the above trade-off has worked in the Solarius\u0027 favor, but anything that can survive the initial alpha strike will be able to make full advantage of the Solarius\u0027 vulnerabilities.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hobbes Novakoff","CreatedById":129018,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T16:50:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222533813\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461429960\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022151034\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NotAnAimbot\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, NotAnAimbot said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you think about this then?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-1.25 cockpits can only carry two .50s, 2 Vulcans or a single GAU-8\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Mk2 cockpits can carry two Vulcans turrets or two GAU-8s\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Mk3 cockpits can carry three GAU-8s, 4 Vulcan turrets or a single laser in the nose\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m \u00A0thinking of being a bit less linear. For instance, GAU-8s and other fixed guns aren\u0027t useful on airliners because it\u0027s like trying to do the Daytona 500 in a segmented bus. I do want a sort of tailgun-type weapon, as 50 cals are far too small and something like the Millennium is too big. Or only putting a restriction on lasers-after all, guns will be less useful against small, nonmoving targets, especially when I start to armor them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Redshift OTF","CreatedById":78679,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T16:52:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLaser boats are susceptible to missiles as they generally don\u0027t have the manoeuvrability to escape them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NotAnAimbot","CreatedById":151034,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T16:54:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222533831\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461430222\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129018\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hobbes Novakoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Hobbes Novakoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsort of tailgun-type\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe B-52 used quad .50s or a M61 Vulcan for their tail turret.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3f/B52_tail_turret.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022B52_tail_turret.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nB-52A\u0027s tail guns made of 4x0.50in guns\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.air-and-space.com/19750316%20Davis-Monthan/75105%20B-52H%2061-0036%20left%20rear%20M61%20Vulcan%20gatling%20gun%20l.jpg\u0022 alt=\u002275105%20B-52H%2061-0036%20left%20rear%20\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLater B-52 with a M61 Vulcan\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T17:15:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222533847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461430348\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278679\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Redshift OTF\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, Redshift OTF said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLaser boats are susceptible to missiles as they generally don\u0027t have the manoeuvrability to escape them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, but they have the laser to escape them. It\u0027s what the laser\u0027s made for, isn\u0027t it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Redshift OTF","CreatedById":78679,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T17:17:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think you can get them to fire at both missiles and the opponent craft though. That\u0027s their weakness.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JollyGreenGI","CreatedById":70652,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-23T17:17:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222533892\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136016\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461431736\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, but they have the laser to escape them. It\u0027s what the laser\u0027s made for, isn\u0027t it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRecently, no. The lasers forfeit the ability to down incoming missiles when set to attack all targets, for some reason.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}